headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Expedia Group (EXPE) After A 56% One Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Expedia Group's share price still offers value after a strong run, you are not alone. This article is designed to help you weigh that up calmly. The stock last closed at US$264.84. While returns over the past 7 days and 30 days show declines of 2.3% and 6.5%, the 1 year and 3 year returns of 56.2% and 124.9% highlight how much the share price has already moved.
